{"id":132860,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/图辑：胡锦涛访美华盛顿团体抗议/","date":"2011-01-20T08:11:00Z","modified":"2011-01-20T08:11:00Z","title":"图辑：胡锦涛访美华盛顿团体抗议","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023040_washington01_bbc_g926.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"支持西藏独立人士在美国白宫外抗议中国国家主席胡锦涛到访（18/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023040_washington01_bbc_g926.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>中国国家主席胡锦涛的专机降落华盛顿前，在白宫外已经举行了不少的抗议者。他们高举标语，上面用英文写着：胡锦涛：失败的领袖。中共：死亡的政党。西藏现在就独立。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023151_washington02_bbc_g926.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"支持西藏独立人士在美国白宫外抗议中国国家主席胡锦涛到访（18/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023151_washington02_bbc_g926.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>他们大多数是为了争取西藏独立的抗议者。这位抗议者举着西藏的旗帜。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023228_washington03_bbc_g926.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"支持西藏独立人士在美国白宫外抗议中国国家主席胡锦涛到访（18/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023228_washington03_bbc_g926.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>抗议者聚集在离白宫不远处的草坪上，高喊口号。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023331_washington04_bbc_g926.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"美国白宫外警察监视支持西藏独立人士抗议（18/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023331_washington04_bbc_g926.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>警察在监视抗议者，但是没有对他们的活动进行干预。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023419_washington05_bbc_g926.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"美国白宫外中国广东访民王永利（左）与儿子王东炎拉起请愿横幅（18/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023419_washington05_bbc_g926.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>示威者也有从中国大陆来的强迫搬迁受害者。广东韶关被强拆户王永利、王东炎父子在白宫前申冤。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023454_washington06_bbc_g926.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"中国广东访民王永利在美国白宫外请愿（18/1/2011）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2011/01/19/110119023454_washington06_bbc_g926.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>王永利说，他跑到华盛顿了申冤是被逼到绝路才这样做的。（图／文：BBC中文网记者伟亮）</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bAYcNlcOlzqGoCEVlcJHI53SdAg/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bAYcNlcOlzqGoCEVlcJHI53SdAg/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bAYcNlcOlzqGoCEVlcJHI53SdAg/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bAYcNlcOlzqGoCEVlcJHI53SdAg/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/BBC/World/~4/lCRivLQgFZo\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<h4>Behind the Great Firewall? <a href=\"http://83920.info\">Click here to create a Psiphon account</a>.</h4>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9991,9781,18836]}